overview: in Lake Hiawatha, New Jersey before 70+ fans: Alicia b Rick Cataldo w/Vinny G from VTG Enterprises to retain the WSU Women's title, Alicia b Nikki Roxx to retain the WSU Women's title, The Soul Sisters (Latasha and Jana w/Missy Hyatt) b Della'Morte and Taylor Nicole w/Liz Savage, Alexa Thatcher b Alere Little Feather, Satan's Sisters (Amy Lee and Luna Vachon) b The Diva Killaz (Kayla Sparks and Miss Deville w/Liz Savage) - Notes: After the match, Amy Lee and Luna Vachon proclaimed themselves as the unofficial WSU Tag Team Champions and asked for real competition, putting out an open challenge.
title: WSU 2nd Ever Girls Show
